                                  @{b}Copyrights@{ub}

This program is subordinated to @{"Standard Amiga FD-Software Copyright Note" link AFD-COPYRIGHT/main 167}.

This program is ShareWare, which is specified in item @{" 4s " link AFD-COPYRIGHT/main 86}.
