@node dist "Distribution"

  I have one exception from AFD-Copyright. It's distribution rights.

  If you want to include MultiView package in your collection you must
write to me for permission and newest versions. Without my permission
MultiView can be included on :
  - Aminet CD-ROM
  - Polish edition of Amiga Magazin on their Cover CD and MA CD series

  Others must have my permission or must send me free copy of their CD or
magazine with Cover CD.
  To include MultiView in any distribution you must include full archive of
MultiView (2b_mv_os2), MultiViewPrefs (2b_mv_prefs) and your local languages
(2b_mv_language or 2b_mv_loc) with all files without renaming.

@endnode
